OL,3,CDrivers in Manchester fined #450,000
OL,4,Cover yellow box junctions
OL,6,FManchester City Council issued more
OL,7,Ffines to drivers caught in yellow box
OL,8,Fjunctions than anywhere else in the
OL,9,Fcountry, new figures show.
OL,11,FThe RAC, which obtained the statistics
OL,12,Fthrough Freedom of Information (FoI)
OL,13,Frequests, said the "enormously high
OL,14,Fnumber" of penalty charge notices
OL,15,F(PCNs) should "send alarm bells
OL,16,Fringing in council offices".
OL,18,FAnalysis shows Manchester City Council
OL,19,Fissued the most PCNs with 13,130 in
OL,20,Frelation to six junctions, bringing in
OL,21,F#446,706.
