OL,4,Cover yellow box junctions
OL,6,FPCNs are generally #70, reduced to #35
OL,7,Fif paid within 21 days.
OL,9,FOnly a fraction of yellow box fines
OL,10,Fare appealed against by drivers, with
OL,11,Fthe highest proportion appealed being
OL,12,F18% in the Manchester City Council
OL,13,Farea.
OL,15,FYellow boxes are used in an attempt to
OL,16,Fensure traffic flows smoothly through
OL,17,Fbusy junctions. Motorists should not
OL,18,Fenter them unless their exit is clear
OL,19,For they are waiting to turn right.
