OL,3,CDrivers in Manchester fined #450,000
OL,4,Cover yellow box junctions
OL,6,FElsewhere, Kent's Medway Council
OL,7,Fraised the second highest amount at
OL,8,F#145,162 after handing out 4,433 PCNs
OL,9,Ffor the five yellow boxes it enforced.
OL,11,FIt was followed by Buckinghamshire
OL,12,FCouncil, which received #139,798 for
OL,13,F3,618 fines.
OL,15,FBut the single junction that generated
OL,16,Fthe largest revenue was at Dennis
OL,17,FRoundabout in Guildford, Surrey, which
OL,18,Fcost drivers #81,445 as 4,250 PCNs
OL,19,Fwere issued.
