OL,4,Cover yellow box junctions
OL,6,FAt the other end of the scale,
OL,7,FGloucestershire County Council issued
OL,8,Fjust 30 yellow box PCNs, raising #945,
OL,9,Fwhile Leeds City Council handed out 50
OL,10,Ffines, resulting in #605 being paid.
OL,12,FRAC senior policy officer Rod Dennis
OL,13,Fsaid a yellow box which generates a
OL,14,Fsmall number of fines indicates it is
OL,15,F"working as it should", which must be
OL,16,Fthe ambition for councils rather than
OL,17,Fusing them as a "revenue-raising
OL,18,Fopportunity".
