OL,6,FHe went on: "Very few people set out
OL,7,Fto deliberately flout the rules and
OL,8,Fget fined.
OL,10,F"The large number of penalties being
OL,11,Fdished out over a small number of
OL,12,Flocations and in a short space of time
OL,13,Fshould send alarm bells ringing in
OL,14,Fcouncil offices.
OL,16,F"It's vital box junctions are used in
OL,17,Fthe correct places and are only as big
OL,18,Fas absolutely necessary.
