OL,6,F"They must be fairly set up so that
OL,7,Fdrivers don't find themselves stranded
OL,8,Fthrough no fault of their own."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the Local
OL,11,FGovernment Association said: "All
OL,12,Fcouncils follow guidance to ensure
OL,13,Fmotorists are treated fairly.
OL,15,F"There are processes for appeal if
OL,16,Fanyone believes they have been
OL,17,Funfairly fined."
OL,19,FManchester City Council was approached
OL,20,Ffor a comment.
